00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:55,300
Doctor Vogel sent me here
to look for Markus

267
00:15:55,433 --> 00:15:57,267
because he was said
to be found here.

268
00:15:57,400 --> 00:16:01,133
Sir, good thing Selena agreed
to stay behind.

269
00:16:01,267 --> 00:16:04,967
She's just scared that the
syndicate might get her again.

270
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,200
You're right, Bok.

271
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:09,167
The truth is, she was just
pretending to be brave.

272
00:16:09,333 --> 00:16:10,967
That's why she came with us
earlier.

273
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:17,133
But the truth is, this stays
between us, okay?

274
00:16:17,267 --> 00:16:18,900
She's only coming with us

275
00:16:19,033 --> 00:16:21,767
because she doesn't want to be
away from me.

276
00:16:25,067 --> 00:16:26,867
Earlier, when we were looking
for Doctor Vogel,

277
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,567
she clung on to me.

278
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:32,900
Of course, you know me,
I already have Cecilia.

279
00:16:33,033 --> 00:16:33,967
But this...

280
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,733
this has been my problem
for a long time already.

281
00:16:35,867 --> 00:16:36,633
Why is it like that?

282
00:16:36,767 --> 00:16:38,433
A lot of girls
have a crush on me.

283
00:16:38,567 --> 00:16:42,700
Actually, since I was a kid,
this has been my problem.

284
00:16:42,867 --> 00:16:45,800
They always tease me because
they have a crush on me.

285
00:16:58,700 --> 00:17:00,800
Any update about Selena?

286
00:17:00,933 --> 00:17:03,567
We still don't have any news
from our guy at Station 12.

287
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:06,333
But I think...

288
00:17:06,467 --> 00:17:08,200
Selena hasn't come home yet.

289
00:17:08,333 --> 00:17:10,133
So we're still safe with boss.

290
00:17:10,267 --> 00:17:11,767
What makes you say that?

291
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:12,933
First of all,

292
00:17:13,067 --> 00:17:16,100
the police officers who followed
you to Milan and Dubai

293
00:17:16,267 --> 00:17:17,967
still haven't come home.

294
00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:20,267
So be careful in Switzerland

295
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,500
because they might still be
after you.

296
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:30,167
That's Markus!

297
00:17:43,133 --> 00:17:43,900
Bok!

298
00:17:44,033 --> 00:17:44,833
Bok!

299
00:17:44,967 --> 00:17:47,433
Bok, maybe it's better
to split up...

300
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:51,400
Enriquez, let's...

301
00:18:40,567 --> 00:18:41,333
Wait!

302
00:18:43,733 --> 00:18:44,700
This is expensive.

303
00:18:45,833 --> 00:18:47,533
500 euros!

304
00:18:50,533 --> 00:18:53,000
500 euros, 500 euros...

305
00:18:53,133 --> 00:18:56,300
Bok, Enriquez, watch.

306
00:18:56,467 --> 00:18:59,200
You won't hit me even once.

307
00:19:07,867 --> 00:19:08,867
Bok!

308
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,033
It's okay, Bok.

309
00:19:10,167 --> 00:19:11,567
I know you didn't mean it.

310
00:19:20,433 --> 00:19:23,633
What? What, what?
Where is he?

311
00:19:34,033 --> 00:19:35,400
- Sir!
- Are you okay?

312
00:19:35,533 --> 00:19:37,700
You fools!

313
00:19:37,833 --> 00:19:42,467
He didn't hit me, but I got hit
by everything you threw at him.

314
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:43,200
Chase him!

315
00:19:43,333 --> 00:19:44,600
Let's go, let's go!

316
00:20:25,767 --> 00:20:26,933
<i> There, at the back.</i>

317
00:20:47,267 --> 00:20:49,667
Sir, come on, let's go inside.

318
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,633
Wait a minute, Enriquez.

319
00:20:50,767 --> 00:20:52,400
What are you doing?
Are you crazy?

320
00:20:52,533 --> 00:20:54,567
We're not familiar
with the inside yet.

321
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:57,633
If we let this go, we might
not save Reign anymore.

322
00:20:57,767 --> 00:20:59,633
If we get into danger,

323
00:20:59,767 --> 00:21:02,533
we won't be able to save
your godsister anymore.

324
00:21:02,667 --> 00:21:04,367
Look, there are guards.

325
00:21:05,533 --> 00:21:07,333
And look at those guards,

326
00:21:07,467 --> 00:21:09,300
they look like they're obsessed
with women.

327
00:21:09,467 --> 00:21:12,067
Too bad, if Selena were here,

328
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:15,033
we could have used her
as a distraction.

329
00:21:15,167 --> 00:21:17,500
After all, she likes
to distract people.

330
00:21:17,633 --> 00:21:22,267
She even tried it on me,
but I have strong self-control.

331
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:25,233
What does she think of me?
Someone who's weak?

332
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:26,500
Of course, I'm not...

333
00:21:32,733 --> 00:21:33,467
Wow...

334
00:21:36,633 --> 00:21:39,167
It's so nice here, right?

335
00:21:41,067 --> 00:21:42,333
But it's really hot.

336
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:47,667
So hot!

337
00:21:48,933 --> 00:21:50,967
I'm so thirsty.

338
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:51,833
What's...

339
00:21:51,967 --> 00:21:52,967
What's being shown?

340
00:21:53,100 --> 00:21:54,200
Let me see.

341
00:21:54,333 --> 00:21:55,567
What's being shown?

342
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:56,800
- Hey.
- Ouch.

343
00:21:57,933 --> 00:21:58,600
Do you have...

344
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:04,900
water, juice, or wine?

345
00:22:09,733 --> 00:22:10,867
Sorry.

346
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:18,167
You guys are shameless.

347
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:21,367
No matter what country you're
in, you guys are perverts!

348
00:22:37,933 --> 00:22:39,967
- Not all guys are perverts!
- Bok!

349
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:42,467
You're ruining the reputation
of men!

350
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:44,867
- Bok, enough.
- Not all guys are perverts!

351
00:23:03,233 --> 00:23:04,433
We need to move fast now.

352
00:23:04,567 --> 00:23:06,267
All the organs are sold already.

353
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,667
Organ harvesting.

354
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:08,600
It's Reign!

355
00:23:08,733 --> 00:23:11,667
Will I ever find someone
like him?

356
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:13,133
That's the type of guy
you're into?

357
00:23:13,267 --> 00:23:14,067
Actually, Bal is cute.

358
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:14,933
Is he your type?

359
00:23:15,067 --> 00:23:16,267
Look at his face. He's ugly!

360
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:22,067
I heard Tonyo didn't come home.

361
00:23:22,233 --> 00:23:23,667
Well, they probably
followed Enriquez.

362
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:24,733
Well, you know him,

363
00:23:24,867 --> 00:23:25,767
he doesn't leave anyone hanging
in mid-air.

364
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,167
For sure, they'll get in trouble
with Chief.

365
00:23:27,300 --> 00:23:28,467
Disobeying direct orders,

366
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:29,933
there's a sanction for that,
right?

367
00:23:30,067 --> 00:23:31,533
I'm sure Conde knows that.

368
00:23:31,667 --> 00:23:33,333
He just couldn't leave
Enriquez behind.

369
00:23:33,467 --> 00:23:37,267
You're ruining everything
I've worked so hard for!
